{"tid":166400,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有電話清潔強迫症?","createTime":"2017-03-22T05:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T04:12:00.000Z","uid":17836,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6fbb49abdcb302b93f0fcb9f3658f565e71c36cc","tid":166400,"uid":17836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"有冇人有電話清潔強迫症? 自完全接受唔到個Mon有油，一定要每日用酒精清潔個Mon。每次用完電話都要用電筒照一照睇下有冇油。"},{"pid":"a69328ee4698261f433f88526b1c4599b3431352","tid":166400,"uid":143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:47:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffffe0ec20ceecfc04e1c161408696ea5e3595b6","tid":166400,"uid":93324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:02:59.000Z","msg":"自從電話污糟過廁所板單新聞 我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0c616afdb4310d1888eaa160ce89320f588bfb","tid":166400,"uid":17966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會係咁拎濕紙巾抹"},{"pid":"65b2dcbffa65ff5733fb1870a7b0550c33d4af61","tid":166400,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:55:08.000Z","msg":"返到屋企會用濕毛錢抹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9fd488cae361988c21234bc40d7ead6b14822b","tid":166400,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返到屋企會用濕毛巾抹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"951cfb22d08651d142ca85174d7a5e54ba5e25b0","tid":166400,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用手絹濕水抹！"},{"pid":"ece836fb642d6e62f02