>\n唔明啲人點解咁鬼污糟<br />\n出街電話周圍放<br />\n夜晚唔消毒就放上床<br />\n真係好污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同人講我晚晚都消毒電話仲被人當怪胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad52f6db83fe387ad1a5ce81e9f88f4089db00ca","tid":166400,"uid":81751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"出街食飯電話一定唔會放檯面<br />\n但係同親fd食飯佢地一拎起我部電話睇完之後就放落檯 我又唔想屌鳩佢地好似好無謂咁 但心諗頂做咩放落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出完街返屋企要用酒精抹乾淨部電話先拎上床用<br />\n一見到個mon有任何污漬就要即刻抹"},{"pid":"2f025d48e028eec5e521a27c471e919e0fe51bc2","tid":166400,"uid":5546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"淨係用水沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce6ef4ac5752cb0458ea7f2d2b0dacc9a68b5a6","tid":166400,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"一定會  不過係一星期一次"},{"pid":"5a64245e7670deea22c95442430a8047e45e61fa","tid":166400,"uid":13327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"沖完涼第一件事<br />\n拎火酒紙巾抹乾淨部電話<br />\n先碌上床<br />\n日日如是  風雨不改"},{"pid":"79facb7792dfdf85394562e9f1f4ad5290fc5642","tid":166400,"uid":34652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:46:42.000Z","msg":"每星期清潔一次喇叭啲塵<br />\n機身日日用濕毛巾/紙巾抹到反光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb9d7d01e30906fff2b96cb470059951ce25458","tid":166400,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"消毒酒精果D唔係傷MON既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc30dc6727437c2c23fc46a05e20bb998dbde9b","tid":166400,"uid":17836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:51:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>消毒酒精果D唔係傷MON既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為用左mon貼，所以唔會傷到本體。"},{"pid":"95011a0acf5514592ce53058daafa7519e315590","tid":166400,"uid":45047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:02:23.000Z","msg":"每日會幫部電話用沐浴露洗白白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nS7嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然真係防水<br />\n但真係怕日日洗遲早會入水收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fd7fa76de48aea55df8f4fab7c0b1bf1e3f71c","tid":166400,"uid":81220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日會幫部電話用沐浴露洗白白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nS7嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然真係防水<br />\n但真係怕日日洗遲早會入水收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前部sony又話防水<br />\n洗左幾日電話就收左皮<br />\n同朋友講仲被人恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2b3e53d1fe81f04eef0fc58e36b8a9c1e677c4","tid":166400,"uid":1637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"成日一有少少污joe 就會即刻拎起件衫係咁抺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37256d7e46d785426fde3bcd1c7c66b793189fb3","tid":166400,"uid":10651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:05:55.000Z","msg":"用口水奶乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b415cbfc61b237c2ceebc00da53d7e4c568cbc0","tid":166400,"uid":43190,"like":0,"dislike